# Get all users.
GET http://localhost:9080/simple-rpg/api/users

### Get one user by its UUID - bad UUID
GET http://localhost:9080/simple-rpg/api/users/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000

### Get one user by its UUID - Bob UUID
GET http://localhost:9080/simple-rpg/api/users/ed6cfb2a-cad7-47dd-9b56-9d1e3c7a4197

### Create user

PUT http://localhost:9080/simple-rpg/api/users/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "login": "test",
  "name": "John",
  "surname": "Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "gender": "MALE"
}

### Create user (bob) avatar

PUT http://localhost:9080/simple-rpg/api/users/ed6cfb2a-cad7-47dd-9b56-9d1e3c7a4197/avatar
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="avatar"; filename="sigrid.png'

< simple-rpg/src/main/resources/pl/edu/pg/eti/kask/rpg/configuration/avatar/zereni.png
